reviewText: This item was listed as new and it is definitely used. No problems with the quality but it wasn't wrapped and two of the booklets had small tears on the back covers.

Excellent. My error was getting them separately  and as a set. The separate ones had companion cd's .The  interesting  is this set featured their tours with their original pianist.and their first tour since his untimely death.
The 82 concert at Leeds is a stinker in my opinion.  The one from 1971 is good but not quite as good as I expected.  The other three in this set are all excellent.
I was blown away with this box set!!! I've seen lots of concerts and this box set was the best of the best.
